casebody.data:
The State ex rel. York, Appellant, v. Industrial Commission of Ohio, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. York v. Indus. Comm., 99 Ohio St.3d 529, 2003-Ohio-4692.]

*530(No. 2002-2070 Submitted April 29, 2003 Decided September 17, 2003.) Becker & Cade and Dennis A. Becker, for appellant. Jim Petro, Attorney General, and Cheryl J. Nester, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed consistent with the opinion of the court of appeals.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton and O’Con-nor, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, J., not participating.
